---
---

<section id="oss" class="py-16 border-b border-(--color-border-subtle)">
  <div class="mx-auto w-[85%] md:w-[60%] max-w-none min-w-[320px]">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
      <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-(--color-text-dim) whitespace-nowrap">
        Open Source
      </span>
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-(--color-border-subtle)"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start">

      <div class="border border-(--color-border-subtle) bg-(--color-surface) p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.01] hover:bg-(--color-bg)">
        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-(--color-text-dim) mb-2">Co-maintainer</p>
        <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-(--color-text-head) mb-3">
          FastAPI-boilerplate
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--color-text-muted) mb-4">
          Batteries-included async FastAPI starter shipping auth (sessions, OAuth, API keys), FastCRUD, Alembic, Taskiq workers, Redis caching, and per-tier rate limiting out of the box, organized as a uv workspace with a vertical-slice module layout. The bp CLI handles Docker Compose generation, env auditing, and third-party plugin mounting, making it the open-source foundation FastroAI extends for full SaaS builds.
          Contributor to documentation and project maintenance.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-(--color-text-muted) mb-4">
          <span class="text-(--color-text-bright)">~2k</span> stars ·
          <span class="text-(--color-text-bright)">286</span> forks
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/benavlabs/FastAPI-boilerplate"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[13px] md:text-[11px] px-3 py-1.5 border border-(--color-border) rounded hover:border-(--color-text-muted) text-(--color-text-muted) hover:text-(--color-text-bright) transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          View on GitHub <span class="inline-block transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5">↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-0 md:pt-2">
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--color-text-muted) mb-4">
          I focus on documentation quality and keeping the project ergonomic for people building real
          FastAPI services. Named co-maintainer in <a href="https://github.com/benavlabs/FastAPI-boilerplate/releases/tag/v0.18.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-(--color-accent-dim) hover:decoration-(--color-accent) transition-colors duration-200">v0.18.0, the pluggable restructure release</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--color-text-muted) mb-4">
          My contributions lean toward developer experience: cleaner abstractions, lower boilerplate, and making the codebase easier to extend. Committed to a contribution surface where adding new things stays seamless.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {['FastAPI', 'SQLAlchemy 2.0', 'Pydantic V2', 'Async Python'].map(t => (
            <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-[3px] border border-(--color-border) text-(--color-text-muted) tracking-wide">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
